# Project Setup

## Objective
Set up the SvelteKit project and required base configuration for Gamified DevHouse.

## Tasks
1. Initialize a SvelteKit project in `client/` directory (if not exists) or standard project root.
2. Install dependencies based on `project.config.yml` (tailwindcss, gsap, supabase-js).
3. Configure `tailwindcss` and layout scaffolding.
4. Establish environment variables `VITE_SUPABASE_URL` and `VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`.
